    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Semiconductor devices used to amplify, control, or modify electrical current. Transistors perform the same function as a vacuum tube while requiring less power and producing less heat.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
